---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nos Services | Jour de Chance" description="Expertise stratégique, Génération de leads et Formation.">
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-20 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Notre Expertise</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">
        Des solutions concrètes pour<br> <span class="text-teal-500">provoquer votre réussite</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Nous combinons stratégie data-driven et outils digitaux pour transformer votre potentiel en résultats mesurables.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 border border-gray-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-teal-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Audit & Stratégie</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Nous analysons votre marché et vos processus actuels pour identifier les opportunités de croissance inexploitées.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Analyse de marché</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Positionnement de marque</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Roadmap digitale</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 border border-gray-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-teal-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Génération de Leads</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Mise en place de systèmes d'acquisition automatisés pour alimenter vos commerciaux en prospects qualifiés.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Campagnes publicitaires</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Landing Pages optimisées</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Automation CRM</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-gray-100 border border-gray-50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-teal-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Formation & Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Faites monter vos équipes en compétence pour qu'elles maîtrisent les outils digitaux modernes.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Ateliers pratiques</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Coaching dirigeant</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500">✓</span> Support technique</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Prêt à changer la donne ?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-10">
        Discutons de vos objectifs et voyons comment nous pouvons vous aider à les atteindre.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl">
        Demander un devis gratuit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
